<link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ 'shortcuts.css' | asset_url }}" media="print" onload="this.media='all'">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ 'shortcuts-responsive.css' | asset_url }}" media="print" onload="this.media='all'">

{% style %}
	.shortcuts-features-item-image-winter {
		background: url({{ 'falling-snow.png' | asset_url }}), lightgray -763px -184.5px / 530.038% 512.5% no-repeat; 
	}
{% endstyle %}

<div class="shortcuts">
	<div class="shortcuts-wrap">
		<div class="shortcuts-title">
			<div class="shortcuts-title-text">Teslogic Shortcuts</div>
			<div class="shortcuts-title-icon">
				<img src="{{ 'shortcuts-top-icon.svg' | asset_url }}">
			</div>	
		</div>
		<div class="shortcuts-subtitle">
			Maximize your driving comfort with an innovative set of commands
		</div>
		<div class="shortcuts-info">
			<div class="shortcuts-info-block shortcuts-info-block-text">
				<div class="shortcuts-info-block-text-primary">"Teslogic Shortcuts" is a set of convenient commands that enable you to manage auxiliary vehicle systems not found in Tesla's basic functionality.</div>
				<div class="shortcuts-info-block-text-secondary">These commands add convenience without affecting the driving process or compromising vehicle safety</div>
			</div>
			<div class="shortcuts-info-block shortcuts-info-block-relative">
				<div class="shortcuts-info-block-background">
					<img src="{{ 'shortcuts-car-bg.png' | asset_url }}">
				</div>
				<div class="shortcuts-info-block-image">
					<img src="{{ 'shortcuts-iphone-desktop.png' | asset_url }}" srcset="{{ 'shortcuts-iphone-retina.png' | asset_url }} 2x" loading="lazy">
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="shortcuts-info-block shortcuts-info-block-between">
				<div class="shortcuts-info-block-between-image shortcuts-info-artboard-image">
					<img src="{{ 'shortcuts-artboard-desktop.png' | asset_url }}" srcset="{{ 'shortcuts-artboard-retina.png' | asset_url }} 2x" loading="lazy">
				</div>
				<div class="shortcuts-info-block-between-text shortcuts-info-artboard-text">
					To activate Shortcuts, you need to switch the Active Control toggle to the "on" position using a pin or any other sharp object.
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="shortcuts-info-block shortcuts-info-block-between">
				<div class="shortcuts-info-block-between-image shortcuts-info-info-image">
					<img src="{{ 'shortcuts-info-icon.svg' | asset_url }}">
				</div>
				<div class="shortcuts-info-block-between-text shortcuts-info-info-text">
					Shortcuts settings and changes are stored within the transmitter, enabling them to function when the phone is disconnected.
				</div>				
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="shortcuts-features">
	    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item">
		    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-image">
		    		<img src="{{ 'shortcuts-image-1-desktop.png' | asset_url }}" srcset="{{ 'shortcuts-image-1-retina.png' | asset_url }} 2x" loading="lazy">
		    	</div>
		    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info">
			    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info-title">
				    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info-title-text">
				    		Battery Preheat<br>for Supercharging
				    	</div>
				    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info-title-icon">
				    		<img src="{{ 'shortcuts-icon-01.svg' | asset_url }}">
				    	</div>			    		
			    	</div>
			    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info-description">
			    		Prepare your Tesla for Supercharging 10-20 minutes before <br>
			    		your scheduled session (not at a Tesla charging station). <br>
			    		Engage the battery preheating function to save time during <br>
			    		charging. Tesla typically preheats the battery before <br>
			    		charging, but this shortcut accelerates the process. The <br>
			    		preheating will automatically deactivate after 40 minutes.
			    	</div>
		    	</div>
	    	</div>
	    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item">
		    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-image">
		    		<img src="{{ 'shortcuts-image-2-desktop.png' | asset_url }}" srcset="{{ 'shortcuts-image-2-retina.png' | asset_url }} 2x" loading="lazy">
		    	</div>
		    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info">
			    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info-title">
				    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info-title-text">
				    		Chill/Sport Mode<br>Switching via Kickdown
				    	</div>
				    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info-title-icon">
				    		<img src="{{ 'shortcuts-icon-02.svg' | asset_url }}">
				    	</div>			    		
			    	</div>
			    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info-description">
			    		In Chill mode, a full-throttle kickdown for 1 second will <br>
			    		seamlessly transition your Tesla into regular Sport mode. If <br>
			    		you refrain from full-throttle driving for 30 seconds, the <br>
			    		vehicle will revert to Chill mode automatically.
			    	</div>
		    	</div>
	    	</div>
	    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item">
		    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-image shortcuts-features-item-image-winter">
		    		<img src="{{ 'shortcuts-image-3-desktop.png' | asset_url }}" srcset="{{ 'shortcuts-image-3-retina.png' | asset_url }} 2x" loading="lazy">
		    	</div>
		    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info">
			    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info-title">
				    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info-title-text">
				    		Wipers Deicing<br>Winter Mode
				    	</div>
				    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info-title-icon">
				    		<img src="{{ 'shortcuts-icon-03.svg' | asset_url }}">
				    	</div>			    		
			    	</div>
			    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info-description">
			    		Activate this mode to lift the wipers to the area  <br>
			    		where warm air from the heater blows through the  <br>
			    		windshield (service mode). When you step on the  <br>
			    		brake to start driving, the wipers will return to their  <br>
			    		normal position.
			    	</div>
		    	</div>
	    	</div>
	    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item">
		    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-image">
		    		<img src="{{ 'shortcuts-image-4-desktop.png' | asset_url }}" srcset="{{ 'shortcuts-image-4-retina.png' | asset_url }} 2x" loading="lazy">
		    	</div>
		    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info">
			    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info-title">
				    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info-title-text">
				    		Regen<br>Settings
				    	</div>
				    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info-title-icon">
				    		<img src="{{ 'shortcuts-icon-04.svg' | asset_url }}">
				    	</div>			    		
			    	</div>
			    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info-description">
			    		Adjust regenerative braking strength to minimize or <br>
			    		completely eliminate sudden traction loss on <br>
			    		slippery roads. This shortcut allows you to customize <br>
			    		regenerative braking to suit your driving conditions.
			    	</div>
		    	</div>
	    	</div>
	    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item">
		    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-image">
		    		<img src="{{ 'shortcuts-image-5-desktop.png' | asset_url }}" srcset="{{ 'shortcuts-image-5-retina.png' | asset_url }} 2x" loading="lazy">
		    	</div>
		    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info">
			    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info-title">
				    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info-title-text">
				    		Ice<br>mode
				    	</div>
				    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info-title-icon">
				    		<img src="{{ 'shortcuts-icon-05.svg' | asset_url }}">
				    	</div>			    		
			    	</div>
			    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info-description">
			    		This mode distributes torque evenly between the <br>
			    		axles in a 50/50 ratio, significantly reducing the <br>
			    		likelihood of skidding on slippery roads.
			    	</div>
		    	</div>
	    	</div>
	    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item">
		    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-image">
		    		<img src="{{ 'shortcuts-image-6-desktop.png' | asset_url }}" srcset="{{ 'shortcuts-image-6-retina.png' | asset_url }} 2x" loading="lazy">
		    	</div>
		    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info">
			    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info-title">
				    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info-title-text">
				    		Traffic Fines<br>Avoidance
				    	</div>
				    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info-title-icon">
				    		<img src="{{ 'shortcuts-icon-06.svg' | asset_url }}">
				    	</div>			    		
			    	</div>
			    	<div class="shortcuts-features-item-info-description">
			    		Automatically reduce your speed to match the maximum <br>
			    		allowable speed limits in areas with enforced speed <br>
			    		restrictions, helping you avoid fines for speeding.
			    	</div>
		    	</div>
	    	</div>
		</div>
	</div>
